# Day 1 - Claude Setup & AI Personality Profile

## 📖 Overview

Today I began my 60 Days of AI Challenge by setting up Claude, creating an AI Personality Profile, and generating a cinematic AI portrait.

## 🎯 Objectives

* Install and explore Claude
* Create a personalized AI Personality Profile
* Generate an AI portrait
* Create a GitHub repository for documenting progress

## ✅ Tasks Completed

* Created a Claude project
* Generated an AI Personality Profile
* Generated a cinematic AI portrait
* Captured screenshots of the work
* Created a public GitHub repository
* Made my first commit

## 💡 Key Learnings

* AI can be used as a learning partner, research assistant, and productivity tool.
* Effective prompts produce better and more personalized outputs.
* Documenting progress publicly helps build accountability and a professional portfolio.

